author: OrchidAlloy
description: Searches images on Gelbooru with slash command and tag completion support.
install_msg:
ðŸ’— __**Booru**__ ```Cog installed. Instructions:
1. Load it with [p]load gelbooru
2. Enable the slash commands with [p]slash enablecog gelbooru
3. Sync slash commands with [p]slash sync
4.Optionally, set a gelbooru api_key and user_id with [p]set api gelbooru api_key,YOUR_API_KEY /// [p]set api gelbooru user_id,YOUR_USER_ID /// [p]reload gelbooru```
short: Searches images on Gelbooru with slash command and tag completion support.
end_user_data_statement: This cog does not store user data.
